rows.label: fev02_210_125_msg0001
rows.name: Tora-kun, what ingredients do you have?

rows.label: fev02_210_125_msg0002
rows.name:
Just what's in that crate there.
Nothing impressive, unfortunately!

rows.label: fev02_210_125_msg0003
rows.name:
We can't really go shopping for
supplies now, so we'll need to
work with whatever's on hand.

rows.label: fev02_210_125_msg0004
rows.name: Let me check, if you don't mind.

rows.label: fev02_210_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Glitterspuds, Sumpkins...
Oh, and here's an Oil
Oyster and Meaty Carrot.

rows.label: fev02_210_125_msg0006
rows.name:
And Hot Oranges too! These are
actually quite decent ingredients.

rows.label: fev02_210_125_msg0007
rows.name:
Everything here can be eaten raw!
Tora normally just eats them as is!

rows.label: fev02_210_125_msg0009
rows.name:
We're pretty much the
same, aren't we...

rows.label: fev02_210_125_msg0011
rows.name:
So Homura, think you can
prepare something with these?
